hủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/Thi%E1%BB%87n-tai-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-b1fXZ6zcojddT24qShYwtw">Thiện tai hành kỳ 2 - 善哉行其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%ADnh-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%8B-ca/poem-_LCWpePDXkg4EpU_D5o3fg">Thính Dương thị ca - 聽楊氏歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C6%AFng-th%E1%BB%8B-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-_di22SUE6xJUP0ng68j1MA">Tống Ưng thị kỳ 1 - 送應氏其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Vi-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-b%C3%ACnh-s%E1%BB%B1-sung-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-C%E1%BB%91c-qu%E1%BA%ADn-ph%C3%B2ng-ng%E1%BB%B1-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-MFF_HoVQ7OCaWWzHCcGVEw">Tống Vi thập lục bình sự sung Đồng Cốc quận phòng ngự phán quan - 送韋十六評事充同谷郡防禦判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A0nh/T%E1%BB%A9-s%E1%BA%A7u-thi/poem-DU-Xoj-ZhfCDiwOq0PYG-A">Tứ sầu thi - 四愁詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A0nh/author-L37GQHbELmLdeisdE7nPzQ">Trương Hành</a>)<br></div>	</div>
